quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  12,70,"Tuma nde o hebilannoo …ďe doŇčle ma…ď…ďe …óen, o wa…ói …ďetirgal ngal ka doŇčngal musi…ó…óo-neene-gooto makko on, refti ewnotoo…óo eewnii: "eeymon yo setee…ďe, Ko on wuy…ďe"."
  12,71,"∆Āe fewtiti e ma…ď…ďe …ďe mbi'i: "Ko hol…óuum katti…óon?""
  12,72,"∆Āe mbi'i: "minn kattike …ďetirde laam…óo on. Hino woodani kala gaddu…óo ngal, doŇčngal ngelooba, ko miin woni pawtii…óo …óuum"."
  12,73,"∆Āe mbi'i: "min ngoo…óndirii Alla, gooŇč…óii ho…óon nganndi min ngaraani bonnugol ka leydi, min laataaki kadi wuy…ďe"."
  12,74,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Ko wonata njo…ďdi makko si tawii ko on fenoo…ďe?""
  12,75,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Njo…ďdi makko: ko kala mo: […óuum] tawaa ka doŇčngal mun, haray ko kaŇčko [tigir] woni njo…ďdi mun. Ko wano non min njo…ďitirta too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"."
  12,76,"[Yuusufu] fu…ó…óori doŇčle ma…ď…ďe …óen ado doŇčngalmusi…ó…óo- neene-gooto makko on; refti o yaltiniri nde ka doŇčngal musi…ó…óo-neene-gooto makko on. Ko wano non men fewjirani Yuusufa, [tawde] o hattantaano nanngude musi…ó…óo-neene-gooto makko on ka sariya laam…óo on, si wonaa hara ko Alla muuyi. Mi…óen …ďantana darajaaji on mo min muuyi. No e dow kala jom-ganndal ganndo [goo]."
  12,77,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Si o wujjii, haray mus…óo- neene-gooto makko wujjiino ko adii". Yuusufu mari …óum ka woŇčkii makko, o fe√Ī√Īinanaani …ďe …óuum. o maaki: "Ko onon …ďuri bon¬īde nokku! Ko Alla …ďuri anndude ko cifoto…óon"."
  12,78,"∆Āe mbi'i: "heyma yo laam…óo on, oo no mari baabiraawo nawyu…óo oggos; ∆īettu gooto e amen lomto makko. Menen men nji'ii ma jeyaa…óo e mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďeen"."